data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER ~ PRICE IMPROVEMENT + FLEXIBLE FINANCE OPTIONS!! Only $1,875 / month for RENT-to-OWN and SELLER FINANCING -or- Assumable at 2.625%. This lovely 2 Bed, 1 Bath + BONUS Rm is in the heart of Manette! A cozy, updated home welcomes much natural light. Enter & you'll find comfortable living, dining & kitchen areas. Enjoy flex-space of a Den/Office & Laundry Rm. 2 Bedrooms share hallway with Full Bath between. There's plenty of parking in the long driveway or off-street parking plus storage in the 1-Car Garage. An accommodating yard for gardening, play, & relaxation - with a fire pit! The included Security System keeps you safe & secure. Near shopping, Seattle Ferries, schools, Naval Base Kitsap. Come see me & make an offer today!
